description: A cartoon sticker depicts a woman dressed as a nun with a rebellious and provocative expression. She has blonde, stylized hair with curled ends peeking out from under her traditional white and dark grey nun's habit. Her left eye is a striking blue, while her right eye is winking suggestively. Her tongue is sticking out in a playful, slightly rude manner, and she has a small mole near her mouth. She is wearing a low-cut dark grey dress beneath the white bib of the nun's habit, a gold cross necklace hangs between her breasts. Her left hand is visible and gesturing a "thumbs down."
